### Query 1 — Individual Herd with AMS Findings + Pre-Submit + Active Registration

**Sources:** Q70 (VWBS_AMS_NOTIFIED_HERD) + Q87 (app_mde_code pre-submit) + Q93 (active registration)
**Used for:** TC-AMS-01 and TC-AMS-02

**Note:** Q70 alone is not sufficient — it returns herds regardless of application status including
Submitted herds. Q87 adds the pre-submit filter (app_mde_code IN 1,2,3). Q93 adds the active
herd registration check (bcus_bus_end_date > SYSDATE). All three must be combined.

```sql
SELECT ams.herd_no,
       ams.scheme_year,
       a.app_mde_code,
       a.mde_desc        AS app_status,
       bbd.bcus_bus_end_date
FROM VWBS_AMS_NOTIFIED_HERD ams
JOIN vwbs_application a
    ON  a.app_herd_no  = ams.herd_no
    AND a.app_year     = ams.scheme_year
    AND a.app_mde_code IN (1, 2, 3)
JOIN vwco_biss_business_details bbd
    ON  bbd.bcus_bus_id    = ams.herd_no
    AND bbd.bcus_role_code = 100
    AND bbd.bcus_bus_end_date > SYSDATE
WHERE ams.scheme_year = 2026
AND   ams.expired     = 0
AND   ROWNUM <= 10
ORDER BY ams.herd_no;
```

