### TC-AMS-01 — Individual Farmer/Agent with Red AMS Findings Sees Panel on Dashboard (Pre-Submit)

**Jira ID:** BISSAGL-X
**Priority:** High
**Type:** Functional
**Component:** Farmer Dashboard
**Round:** Round 1 — 2026
**Labels:** AMS, FarmerDashboard, Round1, PreSubmit, Individual, TestOnly

**Description:**
Verifies that when an individual farmer or their agent logs into BISS pre-submit and their herd
has Red AMS findings from Round 1, the AMS Findings panel is displayed on the Farmer Dashboard
with all required elements. The panel must show the correct header “AMS findings”, the AMS
status section, a red triangle warning icon labelled “AMS findings”, a “Response required” label
with a red symbol, the count of red notifications, and a green “Respond to findings” button.
Clicking the button must navigate to the AMS screen. The panel must also display the updated
2026 message: “You have until 8 July 2026 to respond to your AMS notifications” — this message
has been changed from last year and must be verified against the new date.

**Test Data:**

- Run **Query 1** to find herd with AMS findings + pre-submit + active registration
- Optionally use **Query 2** for herd with both AMS and PC findings
- Optionally use **Query 3** for herd with specifically AA type AMS error
- Run **Query 6** (BISS_INET) to get agent login

**Preconditions:**

- Herd has at least 1 Red AMS finding in Round 1 (Query 1 result)
- Application is Pre-Submit — Not Started (app_mde_code=1) or Draft (app_mde_code=3)
- Herd registration is active — bcus_bus_end_date > SYSDATE
- Agent login resolved via Query 6

**Test Steps:**

|# |Action                                          |Expected Result                                                                    |
|--|------------------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|1 |Navigate to BISS login page                     |Login page displayed                                                               |
|2 |Log in with agent username, password and OTP    |Successfully authenticated                                                         |
|3 |Click on Basic Income Support for Sustainability|BISS Home page displayed                                                           |
|4 |Navigate to My Clients via left menu            |My Clients page displayed                                                          |
|5 |Search for herd number from Query 1             |Herd appears in results with Not Started or Draft status                           |
|6 |Click herd to open Farmer Dashboard             |Farmer Dashboard displayed                                                         |
|7 |Locate AMS Findings panel on dashboard          |Panel is **visible** on Farmer Dashboard                                           |
|8 |Verify panel header                             |Header reads exactly **“AMS findings”**                                            |
|9 |Verify AMS status section                       |AMS status section displayed underneath header                                     |
|10|Verify red triangle icon                        |Red triangle (⚠) icon visible with label **“AMS findings”**                        |
|11|Verify Response Required label                  |**“Response required”** label displayed with red symbol to the right               |
|12|Verify notification count                       |**“Amount”** label with correct number of Red notifications matching Query 1 result|
|13|Verify Respond to findings button               |Green **“Respond to findings”** button is visible                                  |
|14|Click Respond to findings button                |Navigates to the AMS screen                                                        |
|15|Navigate back to Farmer Dashboard               |Dashboard displayed                                                                |
|16|Verify deadline message                         |Panel shows: **“You have until 8 July 2026 to respond to your AMS notifications”** |
|17|Confirm date is updated from last year          |Message does NOT show last year’s deadline date                                    |

**Pass Criteria:**

- AMS Findings panel visible ✓
- Header, icon, label, count, button all present and correctly labelled ✓
- Button navigates to AMS screen ✓
- Count matches DB result ✓
- Message reads 8 July 2026 — updated from last year ✓

